<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>国土报最新头条</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 22 Oct 2023 08:07:59 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>法国和加拿大情报机构称，造成加沙医院爆炸的是巴勒斯坦火箭弹，而不是以色列空袭</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-22/ty-article/french-canadian-intelligence-say-palestinian-rocket-caused-gaza-hospital-blast/0000018b-560f-dc3c-a5df-deafdee30000</link><description>法国情报官员表示，哈马斯武器库中的几枚火箭弹携带的炸药重量与此相当，其中包括一枚伊朗制造的火箭和一枚巴勒斯坦制造的火箭。法国官员补充说，他们的情报均未表明以色列发动了袭击</description><pubDate>Sun, 22 Oct 2023 07:05:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-22/ty-article/french-canadian-intelligence-say-palestinian-rocket-caused-gaza-hospital-blast/0000018b-560f-dc3c-a5df-deafdee30000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军准备对加沙进行地面入侵，美国将在中东部署防空系统</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-22/ty-article-live/israel-and-hezbollah-trade-fire-in-northern-border-idf-gears-up-for-gaza-ground-invasion/0000018b-554b-d5d2-afef-d5ff03e00000</link><description>以色列军队对从黎巴嫩边境逼近的恐怖分子嫌疑人进行空袭 ■ 自第二次起义以来，以色列国防军首次在约旦河西岸使用战斗机 ■ 靠近黎巴嫩边境的另外 14 个以色列城镇将被疏散 ■ 意大利总理、塞浦路斯总统对以色列进行短暂访问 ■自 10 月 7 日以来，至少有 1,300 人被哈马斯杀害 ■ 哈马斯管理的卫生部：4,137 名巴勒斯坦人被杀，13,000 人受伤</description><pubDate>Sun, 22 Oct 2023 04:20:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-22/ty-article-live/israel-and-hezbollah-trade-fire-in-northern-border-idf-gears-up-for-gaza-ground-invasion/0000018b-554b-d5d2-afef-d5ff03e00000</guid></item><item><title>以色列士兵报告称，在以色列国防军内获得精神支持的机会有限，寻求平民治疗</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-22/ty-article/.premium/israeli-soldiers-report-limited-access-to-mental-support-in-idf-seek-civilian-treatment/0000018b-539d-d1d7-ab8b-7fdfb8b80000</link><description>一位创伤专家表示，以色列军队没有采取积极措施来预防创伤，只是等待士兵寻求帮助。专业人士警告说，如果不采取积极措施为他们提供情感支持，许多以色列士兵将很难重返岗位。</description><pubDate>Sun, 22 Oct 2023 03:42:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-22/ty-article/.premium/israeli-soldiers-report-limited-access-to-mental-support-in-idf-seek-civilian-treatment/0000018b-539d-d1d7-ab8b-7fdfb8b80000</guid></item><item><title>底特律犹太教堂主席被发现在家外被刺死</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-10-22/ty-article/.premium/detroit-synagogue-president-found-stabbed-to-death-outside-her-home/0000018b-553c-df6e-a5db-757e496f0000</link><description>40 岁的萨曼莎·沃尔 (Samantha Woll) 是底特律的一位民主党活动家和著名的犹太教非宗教领袖，她在家外被刺死。犹太社区消息人士称，他们没有任何信息表明这是一起与以色列对哈马斯战争引发的紧张局势有关的仇恨犯罪</description><pubDate>Sun, 22 Oct 2023 02:47:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-10-22/ty-article/.premium/detroit-synagogue-president-found-stabbed-to-death-outside-her-home/0000018b-553c-df6e-a5db-757e496f0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军准备逐步、侵略性地入侵加沙 — — 以及以色列领导层的分裂</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-22/ty-article/.premium/idf-gears-for-a-gradual-aggressive-gaza-invasion-and-a-split-israeli-leadership/0000018b-53d3-dc3c-a5df-dffbd1000000</link><description>以色列军队打算发起加沙地面行动，但面临成功可能性和拜登政府限制的质疑，引发内塔尼亚胡内阁的辩论。以色列国防军高层感觉他们有一次杀戮和被杀的一次性通行证，以恢复之前的正常状态</description><pubDate>Sun, 22 Oct 2023 02:28:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-22/ty-article/.premium/idf-gears-for-a-gradual-aggressive-gaza-invasion-and-a-split-israeli-leadership/0000018b-53d3-dc3c-a5df-dffbd1000000</guid></item><item><title>以色列将所有阿拉伯人视为敌人，除非事实证明并非如此。即便如此，怀疑依然存在</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-22/ty-article/.premium/israel-labels-all-arabs-as-enemies-until-proven-otherwise-even-then-suspicion-lingers/0000018b-52c6-df6e-a5db-76e6a0ff0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Sun, 22 Oct 2023 00:01:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-22/ty-article/.premium/israel-labels-all-arabs-as-enemies-until-proven-otherwise-even-then-suspicion-lingers/0000018b-52c6-df6e-a5db-76e6a0ff0000</guid></item><item><title>这场运动现在正如火如荼地进行：指责死者和人质，为内塔尼亚胡开脱</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-22/ty-article-opinion/.premium/the-campaign-is-in-full-swing-blame-the-dead-and-the-hostages-exonerate-netanyahu/0000018b-5328-d5d2-afef-d7fdaadc0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Sat, 21 Oct 2023 22:57:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-22/ty-article-opinion/.premium/the-campaign-is-in-full-swing-blame-the-dead-and-the-hostages-exonerate-netanyahu/0000018b-5328-d5d2-afef-d7fdaadc0000</guid></item><item><title>由于内塔尼亚胡的立场仍然不确定，卡塔尔施加影响释放美国和以色列人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-22/ty-article/.premium/qatar-exerts-sway-to-release-u-s-israeli-hostages-as-netanyahus-stance-remains-iffy/0000018b-5387-d5d2-afef-d7ff488c0000</link><description>两名美国人质的释放是哈马斯和以色列之间间接谈判的一个试验气球。过去两周，卡塔尔主导了与哈马斯的密集会谈，并与以色列官员保持联系</description><pubDate>Sat, 21 Oct 2023 22:37:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-22/ty-article/.premium/qatar-exerts-sway-to-release-u-s-israeli-hostages-as-netanyahus-stance-remains-iffy/0000018b-5387-d5d2-afef-d7ff488c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列通讯部长在战争中发挥作用：压制媒体</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/editorial/2023-10-22/ty-article/.premium/israels-communication-minister-takes-on-a-role-in-the-war-effort-silencing-the-media/0000018b-539b-df6e-a5db-77ff510e0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Sat, 21 Oct 2023 22:09:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/editorial/2023-10-22/ty-article/.premium/israels-communication-minister-takes-on-a-role-in-the-war-effort-silencing-the-media/0000018b-539b-df6e-a5db-77ff510e0000</guid></item><item><title>拯救以色列人质。尽快释放巴勒斯坦囚犯</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-22/ty-article-opinion/.premium/save-the-israeli-hostages-release-palestinian-prisoners-quickly/0000018b-5329-df6e-a5db-776f12370000</link><description></description><pubDate>Sat, 21 Oct 2023 21:17:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-22/ty-article-opinion/.premium/save-the-israeli-hostages-release-palestinian-prisoners-quickly/0000018b-5329-df6e-a5db-776f12370000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队：加沙北部数十座建筑物遭到袭击，为地面行动做准备</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-21/ty-article/.premium/idf-dozens-of-buildings-in-northern-gaza-struck-in-preparation-for-ground-operation/0000018b-5392-df6e-a5db-77f6677d0000</link><description>随着以色列和哈马斯之间的战争进入第三周，以色列国防军继续对北部地带进行大规模空袭，为地面入侵做准备</description><pubDate>Sat, 21 Oct 2023 18:58:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-21/ty-article/.premium/idf-dozens-of-buildings-in-northern-gaza-struck-in-preparation-for-ground-operation/0000018b-5392-df6e-a5db-77f6677d0000</guid></item><item><title>香烟烧伤、殴打、性侵犯未遂：定居者和士兵虐待巴勒斯坦人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-21/ty-article-magazine/.premium/beatings-burns-attempted-sexual-assault-settlers-and-soldiers-abused-palestinians/0000018b-530f-d1d7-ab8b-7f5fca1d0000</link><description>在瓦迪阿斯西克遭到袭击一周后，巴勒斯坦人和以色列活动人士努力恢复，并指责一支军队是“山顶青年”和定居者。陆军已解除该部队指挥官职务并展开调查</description><pubDate>Sat, 21 Oct 2023 18:13:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-21/ty-article-magazine/.premium/beatings-burns-attempted-sexual-assault-settlers-and-soldiers-abused-palestinians/0000018b-530f-d1d7-ab8b-7f5fca1d0000</guid></item><item><title>开罗和平峰会结束，以色列与加沙地带未取得突破</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2023-10-21/ty-article/cairo-peace-summit-ends-without-israeli-gaza-breakthrough/0000018b-52f8-dc3c-a5df-def8f4bb0000</link><description>阿拉伯领导人要求结束长达数十年的暴力循环，敦​​促重新努力实现以巴和平 ■ 阿巴斯表示巴勒斯坦人不会离开他们的土地</description><pubDate>Sat, 21 Oct 2023 16:24:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2023-10-21/ty-article/cairo-peace-summit-ends-without-israeli-gaza-breakthrough/0000018b-52f8-dc3c-a5df-def8f4bb0000</guid></item><item><title>因担心网络攻击，几家以色列医院被要求切断互联网访问</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-21/ty-article/.premium/several-israeli-hospitals-asked-to-cut-off-internet-access-over-cyberattack-fears/0000018b-52a7-df6e-a5db-76e7892a0000</link><description>以色列卫生部的一份官方声明表示，他们正在“暂时切断互联网连接”，作为一系列“自发行动”的一部分，以“加强医院抵御袭击的能力”</description><pubDate>Sat, 21 Oct 2023 15:55:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-21/ty-article/.premium/several-israeli-hospitals-asked-to-cut-off-internet-access-over-cyberattack-fears/0000018b-52a7-df6e-a5db-76e7892a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军机袭击约旦河西岸的哈马斯地下组织；以色列国防军司令：“我们将进入加沙”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-21/ty-article-live/two-released-american-hostages-arrive-in-israel-idf-continues-attacking-hezbollah-targets/0000018b-5011-dc3c-a5df-dcb9baa70000</link><description>以色列和黎巴嫩边境爆发交火，造成以色列国防军士兵重伤，真主党报告称有六人死亡 ■ 以色列国防军拦截了一枚来自黎巴嫩的地对空导弹 ■ 自战争开始以来，人道主义援助首次进入加沙地带，而联合国表示这还不够 ■ 意大利总理在以色列会见内塔尼亚胡 ■ 自 10 月 7 日以来，至少有 1,300 名以色列人被杀 ■ 哈马斯：4,137 名巴勒斯坦人被杀，约 13,000 人受伤 ■ 85 名巴勒斯坦人在约旦河西岸被杀</description><pubDate>Sat, 21 Oct 2023 04:01:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-21/ty-article-live/two-released-american-hostages-arrive-in-israel-idf-continues-attacking-hezbollah-targets/0000018b-5011-dc3c-a5df-dcb9baa70000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡加沙失败的秘诀：无所作为</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-21/ty-article-opinion/.premium/the-secret-to-netanyahus-gaza-failure-do-nothing/0000018b-4e41-dbe0-a38b-cff5a0de0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Sat, 21 Oct 2023 01:30:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-21/ty-article-opinion/.premium/the-secret-to-netanyahus-gaza-failure-do-nothing/0000018b-4e41-dbe0-a38b-cff5a0de0000</guid></item><item><title>白宫澄清：拜登并未将延迟的加沙地面入侵与释放人质联系起来</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-21/ty-article/.premium/white-house-clarifies-biden-didnt-link-delayed-gaza-ground-invasion-with-hostage-release/0000018b-4f9e-dbe0-a38b-cffe28510000</link><description>此前有报道称，在卡塔尔斡旋下释放两名美国人质后，拜登确认希望以色列推迟对加沙的地面入侵</description><pubDate>Sat, 21 Oct 2023 00:46:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-21/ty-article/.premium/white-house-clarifies-biden-didnt-link-delayed-gaza-ground-invasion-with-hostage-release/0000018b-4f9e-dbe0-a38b-cffe28510000</guid></item><item><title>放弃人质将摧毁以色列社会的最终纽带</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-21/ty-article-opinion/.premium/forsaking-the-hostages-will-destroy-the-final-bond-holding-israeli-society-together/0000018b-4e98-d0de-a7ab-efffdb0e0000</link><description>以色列家庭总是同意将孩子送去军队，相信国家会不惜一切代价来保护他们。加沙 200 名人质被遗弃将颠覆这一局面</description><pubDate>Fri, 20 Oct 2023 22:04:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-21/ty-article-opinion/.premium/forsaking-the-hostages-will-destroy-the-final-bond-holding-israeli-society-together/0000018b-4e98-d0de-a7ab-efffdb0e0000</guid></item><item><title>加沙的以色列人质被困在人道主义援助和地面袭击之间</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-20/ty-article/.premium/israeli-hostages-in-gaza-are-trapped-between-humanitarian-aid-and-a-ground-assault/0000018b-4d76-dbe0-a38b-cdf66bdb0000</link><description>以停火换取人质意味着哈马斯得到缓刑，但许多以色列人不想听到这个消息。尽管如此，埃及、土耳其、卡塔尔和德国仍在努力达成协议</description><pubDate>Fri, 20 Oct 2023 20:16:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-20/ty-article/.premium/israeli-hostages-in-gaza-are-trapped-between-humanitarian-aid-and-a-ground-assault/0000018b-4d76-dbe0-a38b-cdf66bdb0000</guid></item><item><title>在卡塔尔的调解下，两名被哈马斯囚禁的美国人质获释</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-20/ty-article/.premium/two-american-hostages-released-from-hamas-captivity-with-qatari-mediation/0